<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; line-height: 1.45; }
  .page { width: 8.5in; min-height: 11in; padding: 0.7in 0.8in; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
  .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-bottom: 14px; border-bottom: 3px solid <%= segmentColor %>; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .logo-block { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .logo-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 8px; background: <%= segmentColor %>; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
  .logo-brand { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a2e; }
  .logo-sub { font-size: 10px; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .doc-type { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: <%= segmentColor %>; }
  .doc-id { font-size: 11px; color: #888; margin-top: 2px; }
  .tracking { background: #f8f9fb; border: 1px solid #e8eaef; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .tracking .k { color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; }
  .tracking .v { color: #1a1a2e; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .section-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: <%= segmentColor %>; margin: 14px 0 8px; padding-bottom: 4px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8eaef; }
  .info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px 20px; }
  .row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; }
  .label { color: #666; font-weight: 600; }
  .val { color: #1a1a2e; font-weight: 700; text-align: right; }
  .legal { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 10px; color: #444; line-height: 1.5; }
  .legal p { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .signature-section { margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #e8eaef; }
  .sig-intro { font-size: 12px; color: #333; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sig-box { border: 2px dashed #4b5563; background: #f9fafb; height: 70px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 6px; }
  .sig-caption { font-size: 10px; color: #374151; margin-top: 6px; }
  .footer { margin-top: 18px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #e8eaef; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 10px; color: #999; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo-block">
      <div class="logo-icon"><%= segmentIcon %></div>
      <div>
        <div class="logo-brand"><%= segmentBrandName %></div>
        <div class="logo-sub">Commercial Insurance Direct</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:right;">
      <div class="doc-type">Bind Confirmation</div>
      <div class="doc-id"><%= submission_public_id %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tracking">
    <div><div class="k">Submission ID</div><div class="v"><%= submission_public_id %></div></div>
    <div><div class="k">Carrier</div><div class="v"><%= carrier_name || "N/A" %></div></div>
    <div><div class="k">Policy Type</div><div class="v"><%= policy_type || "N/A" %></div></div>
    <div><div class="k">Date</div><div class="v"><%= issued_on || "" %></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Insured Information</div>
  <div class="info-grid">
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Business Name</span><span class="val"><%= business_name || "N/A" %></span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Contact</span><span class="val"><%= contact_name || "N/A" %></span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Email</span><span class="val"><%= client_email || "N/A" %></span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Phone</span><span class="val"><%= client_phone || "On file" %></span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Policy Details</div>
  <div class="info-grid">
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Annual Premium</span><span class="val">$<%= annual_premium %></span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Payment Method</span><span class="val"><%= payment_method === "monthly" ? "Monthly Installments" : "Annual (Pay in Full)" %></span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Effective Date</span><span class="val"><%= effective_date || "N/A" %></span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Expiration Date</span><span class="val"><%= expiration_date || "N/A" %></span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="legal">
    <p><strong>Authorization to Bind.</strong> By signing this document, the insured authorizes Commercial Insurance Direct to bind the policy shown above with <%= carrier_name || "the carrier" %> effective on the stated date.</p>
    <p><strong>Premium and Terms.</strong> The insured acknowledges premium obligations and confirms this request is based on the reviewed quote packet and carrier terms.</p>
    <p><strong>Representations.</strong> The insured represents that submission and underwriting information is accurate to the best of their knowledge.</p>
    <p><strong>Policy Controls.</strong> The issued carrier policy controls final terms, limitations, and exclusions.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-section">
    <div class="sig-intro">
      By signing, I confirm review of submission <strong><%= submission_public_id %></strong> and authorize bind with <strong><%= carrier_name || "the carrier" %></strong>.
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;color:#777;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;">Electronic Signature Area</div>
    <div class="sig-box"></div>
    <div class="sig-caption">BoldSign signature block is applied inside this box.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <span>Commercial Insurance Direct</span>
    <span><%= segmentDomain %></span>
    <span><%= submission_public_id %></span>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

